坦维尔·阿夫扎尔（{{lang-en|'''Tanwir Afzal'''}}；{{bd|1988年|6月12日}}）是一名香港板球運動員。2014年他代表[[香港板球男子代表隊|香港]]參加[[2014年板球世界盃|2014年板球世界盃]]<ref name="Cricinfo">{{Cite web | url=http://www.espncricinfo.com/pakistan/content/player/260036.html | title=Tanwir Afzal | accessdate=21 March 2014 | work=ESPN Cricinfo | archive-date=2017-07-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170721215953/http://www.espncricinfo.com/pakistan/content/player/260036.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年5月1日首次參加[[單日國際賽|單日國際賽]]，在[[2014年ACC超級聯賽|2014年ACC超級聯賽]]迎戰阿富汗<ref name="ODI">{{cite web |url=http://www.espncricinfo.com/ci/engine/match/736497.html |title=Asian Cricket Council Premier League, 2014 |accessdate=26 November 2014 |work=ESPN Cricinfo |archive-date=2017-07-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170707154831/http://www.espncricinfo.com/ci/engine/match/736497.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2015年5月他被任命為香港隊隊長參加[[2014年T20世界盃|2014年T20世界盃]]資格賽<ref name="HKSquad">{{cite web |url=http://www.espncricinfo.com/hkg/content/story/881693.html |title=Afzal to lead Hong Kong in World T20 Qualifier |accessdate=28 May 2015 |work=ESPNCricinfo |archive-date=2019-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191008052106/http://www.espncricinfo.com/hkg/content/story/881693.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2018年8月，他入選香港隊參加[[2018年板球亞洲盃資格賽|2018年板球亞洲盃資格賽]]<ref name="HKACQ">{{cite web |url=http://www.hkcricket.org/en/media/news/hong-kong-squad-for-the-acc-asia-cup-qualifiers-2018-%EF%BC%8D-27th-august-8th-september-2018 |title=Hong Kong Squad for the ACC Asia Cup Qualifiers 2018 － 27th August - 8th September 2018 |work=Hong Kong Cricket |accessdate=4 August 2018 |archive-date=2018-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180804200907/http://www.hkcricket.org/en/media/news/hong-kong-squad-for-the-acc-asia-cup-qualifiers-2018-%EF%BC%8D-27th-august-8th-september-2018 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>並出線，獲得資格參加[[2018年板球亞洲盃|2018年板球亞洲盃]]，而他亦有參賽<ref name="2018AC">{{cite web |url=http://www.hkcricket.org/en/media/news/anshuman-rath-to-lead-hong-kong-into-the-2018-unimoni-asia-cup |title=Anshuman Rath to lead Hong Kong into the 2018 Unimoni Asia Cup |work=Hong Kong Cricket |accessdate=10 September 2018 |archive-date=2018-12-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225011834/http://www.hkcricket.org/en |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

2018年12月，他再次入選港隊參加[[2018年ACC新秀隊亞洲盃|2018年ACC新秀隊亞洲盃]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hkcricket.org/en/media/news/aizaz-khan-to-replace-injured-anshuman-rath-as-captain-for-emerging-nations-cup |title=Aizaz Khan to replace injured Anshuman Rath as captain for Emerging Nations Cup! |work=Hong Kong Cricket |accessdate=3 December 2018 |archive-date=2018-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181204005753/http://www.hkcricket.org/en/media/news/aizaz-khan-to-replace-injured-anshuman-rath-as-captain-for-emerging-nations-cup |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2019年4月，他亦代表港隊參加在納米比亞[[2019年板球世界乙級聯賽|2019年板球世界乙級聯賽]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.icc-cricket.com/media-releases/1173815 |title=All to play for in last ever World Cricket League tournament |work=International Cricket Council |accessdate=11 April 2019 |archive-date=2019-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190411074825/https://www.icc-cricket.com/media-releases/1173815 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。

